result.name: Peking Garden

reviews.text: Located in Yoho Mall this restaurant is very good for their specialty, Peking duck.  The duck is very big and tasty and they do not cheap out on the skin.  Side dishes included crab claws which were very good, xiao long nap, radish cakes and a couple stir fry dishes.  Overall all the dishes were good.  Service was a bit slow and restaurant comfort was mediocre as the air con lacked.
除片皮鴨外 無乜特別
食物可以 但太多人等位

reviews.text: It is fun to walk around. You can have a good shopping experience here. Also, you can try different favor of foods.
A energetic mall that can spend you a day.

reviews.author_name: SpringIDEA泉新平面及室內設計公司
reviews.text: So many kind of shop.  All product are high quality.
it has good clothing items and also make up booths. They also have pop up shops sometimes

Mall 2 has sports shops such as gigasports with ok range of speed and arena brand swimming goggles and budget food options such as maccas and cafe de coral. To get there u have to walk through a ridiculous car park from yoho 1 if u come from mtr. U have to go up one level from mtr level to get there and u will most likely get lost even though it is simple layout. Cinema at one end of yoho 1 with yata.
